description:
76 pages of Marvel Universe action! Three awesome stories!

The Silver Surfer bends time and space to save the people of Newhaven! Prepare yourself for the most mind-bending story in the history of comics!!! By Dan Slott and Michael Allred!

Daredevil matches his skills against San Francisco's new Man Without Fear: The Stunt-Master! By Mark Waid and Chris Samnee!

The Agents of SHIELD invade the domain of the dread Dormammu! By Mark Waid and Paul Renaud!

Featuring material first printed in Daredevil #11, SHIELD #6 and Silver Surfer #11.

76 pages of Marvel Universe adventure! Three amazing stories!

A helpless Daredevil must face one of his worst enemies: the merciless Killgrave! By Mark Waid and Chris Samnee!

SHIELD agent Melinda May teams up with the Scarlet Witch! More action from Mark Waid and Mike Choi!

The Silver Surfer and Dawn face the one being the Surfer cannot possibly defeat: the dreaded Galactus! By Dan Slott and Michael Allred!

Featuring material first printed in Daredevil #10, SHIELD #5 and Silver Surfer #9-10.
